flowchart LR

  U[User] -->|Request / Response| FE[React SPA]

  FE -->|API Request credentials: include| API[Django API Container]

  API -->|Read / Write| DB[(PostgreSQL Container)]
  API -->|Cache| REDIS[(Redis Container)]
  API -->|File Upload| S3[(AWS S3)]

  API -->|Set-Cookie: access & refresh HttpOnly| FE
  FE -->|Auto-send Cookie on Request| API

  DEV[Developer] --> GIT[GitHub]
  GIT --> CI[GitHub Actions]
  CI -->|Build Docker Image| REG[(Docker Registry)]
  REG -->|Deploy| API